data.description: Need a place for the in-laws? This block beauty awaits you. Main house is 4/2 with private master that has a jetted tub. Split level block home. Main level has the kitchen and living area. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms and a bathroom. Downstairs sports a huge master suite with a jetted tub and it's own entrance! Hot tub outside in back. Two long driveways for your toys. Lots of creature comforts here. Home sits high and dry! Shed in back for extra storage. Pics 15-20 are of the in-law suite. If privacy for the in-laws is what you need, this home is for you!
